      "updated": 1776014578595,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Observer patter :- we have observable and observerrs, once the state of the observable is change\nsimple that will update the all the observers ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Observer patter :- we have observable and observerrs, once the state of the observable is change\nsimple that will update the all the observers ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "-syNhmgP1wyoywGtyTmrd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 381.9272738370029,
      "y": 543.9636369185014,
      "width": 835.5794677734375,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
